%e A007846 Examples for description #3. n=3: Place step #3 on each of six possible nearest neighbor (NN) sites of the 4 n=2 configurations given below for description #1. Total instances = 4 X 6 = 24. n=4: Place step #4 on each of 8 NN sites of 8 (straight line) configurations of the form 123. Place step #4 on each of 7 NN sites of 16 configurations of the form 12/3 (with the 3 under the 1). Total instances = 8 X 8 + 7 X 16 = 176.
%Y A007846 If the numbers are constrained to be on a line: A000079, in a square array: A087518, in an n X k array: A087783.
